ALGORITHM IsPalindrome(x)

PROBLEM DESCRIPTION:
Check if the given integer x is a palindrome.

    INPUT:
        x: an integer
    OUTPUT:
        a boolean value indicating whether x is a palindrome or not

    BEGIN:
        Convert x to a string representation: s <- convertToString(x)

        IF s is equal to its reverse THEN
            RETURN true
        ELSE
            RETURN false
        END IF
    END
